Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.70,0:00:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Unfortunately... she's only going to live 'til next spring...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:05.87,0:00:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We came to make sure her fate wouldn't be changed, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:09.65,0:00:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Mitsuki can now turn into the sixteen-year-old {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.74,0:00:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When she told her manager \Nand her doctor about it...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.11,0:00:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it seems like they somewhat believed her...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, then...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I wonder what's going to happen today.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.90,0:00:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.64,0:00:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.10,0:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:23.68,Episode Title,,0,0,0,Sign,{\pos(325,340)\bord2.5}Meroko, Left Alone
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.06,0:01:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You sure you didn't forget anything?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:26.02,0:01:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:27.09,0:01:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't it wonderful how you're getting out so early?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:32.53,0:01:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}D-Dr. Wakaouji!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.32,0:01:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you for taking care of her!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:38.53,0:01:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}S-Sure...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:39.94,0:01:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Madam told me to pass on her appreciation.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:44.83,0:01:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.25,0:01:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I feel great!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:48.36,0:01:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sensei, thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.35,0:01:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're still keeping the fact that you can \Nchange a secret from your grandma, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:58.26,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.68,0:02:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:01.39,0:02:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Him, too?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.52,0:02:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:04.19,0:02:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well then... take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, Dr. Wakaouji.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.94,0:02:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Once I've gotten her settled in...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:11.07,0:02:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-That's okay...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:12.07,0:02:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I have a patient to examine.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:13.69,0:02:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks, though.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:17.12,0:02:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That doctor...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...seems like he doesn't like me...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.79,0:02:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-That's just your imagination!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:22.00,0:02:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh well...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't help it if he hates me.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After all... I'm a Shinigami, and he's a doctor.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:30.63,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Madam was so worried about you...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was quite surprised.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:35.51,0:02:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:40.35,0:02:41.57,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Grandma...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.91,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You still care so much about me...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.02,0:02:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please consider just how much you've \Nimposed upon those who care about you!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.31,0:02:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}First, Dr. Wakaouji had to take care of you.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:50.69,0:02:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone was running around looking for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.93,0:02:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Be more careful about your health.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.06,0:03:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How are you feeling, Grandma?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's just the heat that's getting me.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There is no need to worry.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll excuse myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90}Congratulations on getting released, Mitsuki. {scale}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:23.57,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you, Ooshige-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.02,0:03:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90}We'll start work again after \Nthings have calmed down, okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.36,0:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Instead of that...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:31.32,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...be sure to apologize to everyone when you come back, okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90}Okay! {scale}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:35.53,0:03:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90}I'll get in touch with you again, then.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.47,0:03:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:39.57,0:03:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey! Stupid kid!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.12,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why the heck doesn't this room have any air conditioning?! {shani: Shinigami are a bit too demanding these days, eh?}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's bad for my throat.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.16,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Besides... we're at a high elevation, so there's a cool breeze.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It isn't cool at all!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.92,0:03:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.55,0:03:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What happened to Meroko? {shani: she became cloud no. 9 :D}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Who knows...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:58.59,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you still mad?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What... you're not mad at her?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's her fault that you lost the audition.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.60,0:04:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko must have had her reasons...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-That's true, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks to Meroko, you...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.56,0:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...because of that, I was able to tell \NWakaouji-sensei and Ooshige-san everthing.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I guess so.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.74,0:04:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All that's left is for Meroko to come back...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where did you go?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.67,0:04:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was just doing my duty as a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto, you're such a jerk!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes, yes?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.61,0:05:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is Mitsuki-san here?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:39.17,0:05:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We all came to see her!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:43.41,0:05:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We were so surprised when we heard you were in the hospital.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... isn't it great that you're all better now?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:49.04,0:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.16,0:05:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.87,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's such a big garden!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's even a pond!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's amazing!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:54.79,0:05:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can we take a look around?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.66,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sure.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, madam.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We have guests?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes, they're all friends of Mitsuki-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:09.06,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is the first time we've had so \Nmany people over... I was so surprised!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.11,0:06:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's a ghost story at our school?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Someone saw one in the gym at our school.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In the dead of night...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:23.60,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In the empty gym...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A basketball goes... {\alpha&HFF&}boom... boom... {alpha-time}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:27.89,0:06:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A basketball goes... boom... {\alpha&HFF&}boom... {alpha-time}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:29.40,0:06:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A basketball goes... boom... boom... {alpha-time}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}P-Please stop.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't take this...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We've found Mitsuki's weakness!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is all it takes, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's 'cause...!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That ghost must be lonely.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why it's waiting for someone to play with.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:44.71,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}'Cause... you can't play basketball by yourself, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's true...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.72,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... could it be...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.42,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Meroko?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You don't have to escort us out.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You shouldn't stain yourself yet.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:07.04,0:07:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks for coming today!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}See you later then!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.64,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Bye, bye!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.17,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Bye, bye!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... what an ordeal!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's about Meroko...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.38,0:07:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Y-You're still talking about that...?!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You know... Meroko's... probably at school...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't want to hear it!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm tired of it...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you here, Meroko?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-This is bad!! {You can't hide, she can see you}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't move!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you all right, Meroko?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.38,0:08:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto hasn't said anything?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.93,0:08:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:13.67,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He won't tell me when I ask him either.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}M-My reason... {\alpha&HFF&}my reason was...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}M-My reason... my reason was...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After all, I didn't get hurt.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:21.67,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's just...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:24.78,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When you're gone...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.48,0:08:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it feels like something's missing... something's wrong...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If the three of us aren't together...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.33,0:08:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If it's not the three of us, together, like before...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it feels lonely.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.91,0:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's go back together!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want to go back too...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want to, but Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:19.58,0:09:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sure that Takuto wants you to come back too.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You think so?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.92,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You shouldn't have come back!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why's that?!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:33.01,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm finally alone with her now!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In other words... you're a third wheel!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.64,0:09:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I can't!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's better for Takuto if I'm not around...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-In any case... I can't go back.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:47.23,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Bye.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:48.26,0:09:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:05.67,0:10:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's hot... {\alpha&HFF&}it's uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:08.43,0:10:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's hot... it's uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:11.09,0:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So hot...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}D-Don't even think about it!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:17.89,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... I haven't said anything yet!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's probably about Meroko anyways.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, you already knew.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, you see...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I want you to go bring Meroko back.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's at school...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look here.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:29.20,0:10:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why do I have to bring her back?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:32.24,0:10:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If she wants to come back, she can come back on her own.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.48,0:10:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.94,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay then?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-That's Meroko's problem.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It wasn't anything I did!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.83,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're right.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did Takuto really say that it was okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:48.58,0:10:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He sure did.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}B-But...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on already...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:53.05,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't know what I should say to him...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.89,0:10:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wouldn't "I'm back!", be enough? {shani: OMG! Best convo between Meroko and Mistsuki! <3}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But I doubt that Takuto would say "Welcome back!"...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:02.90,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're still saying that!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.76,0:11:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you keep thinking like that... things will be like this forever!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is that okay with you?!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Not really, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What a blue sky!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And white clouds, too!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey Takuto, come look!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No point.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Besides... Shinigami...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...don't have "blue skies" or "white clouds", you know. {shani: yet they demand air conditioning :D}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.70,0:11:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-Is that so...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.38,0:11:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.55,0:11:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko, come over here!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The two of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hello, Tomoe-chan?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:53.90,0:11:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I have a hypothetical question for you...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.95,0:12:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If two good friends aren't talking to each other...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:04.07,Notice 1 (Ep. 20),,0,0,0,Sign,{\fax0.113\pos(190,135)\frz53.19}Clear Weather
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.92,0:12:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe you could set them up?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:04.22,0:12:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\fscy90\fscx90}What do you mean by set them up?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.54,0:12:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anything works.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you set them up...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90}...the rest is up to them.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Set them up, huh...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.00,0:12:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you going to stay on the phone forever?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't a lengthy phone call a hassle for your friend?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.52,0:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, Tomoe-chan?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:31.15,0:12:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't mind.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:32.54,0:12:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:35.68,0:12:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Make sure you're ready in case of a fire.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.24,0:12:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Have some water nearby.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.24,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Fireworks with her firends, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:47.22,0:12:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... please excuse me.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was too forward.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There is nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I suppose so.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.08,0:12:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.93,0:12:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}By the way...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:56.75,0:13:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}May I go and prepare something for the children?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:07.73,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Real fireworks?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I have a fireworks set...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...but I want ones that go {\i1}Kaboom{\i0} !
Dialogue: 2,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I guess it's all right...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll be counting on you then!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Real fireworks?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:23.20,0:13:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just one of the ones that goes {\i1}Kaboom{\i0} !
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.06,0:13:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I suppose it's okay...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}May we come in?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:33.63,0:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah! Welcome!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.38,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Excuse us for imposing!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good evening.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-chan's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:41.47,0:13:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come... it's this way.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-What is this?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:46.13,0:13:50.72,Note,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fad(210,210)}(Soumen Nagashi [Floating Noodles]: A summer festival activity where people sit at a trough and pick out noodles for dipping.)
Dialogue: 2,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A long Soumen!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:47.93,0:13:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please... eat up, everyone!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This feels so nostalgic!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, hey. You can eat soumen with ginger, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:57.02,0:13:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? Our family uses mayonnaise, though.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Welcome!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.70,0:14:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So cute!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You look beautiful, Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}R-Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks for inviting us today!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.62,0:14:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's about time to begin!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:15.45,0:14:16.54,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Catch!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:20.04,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fad(0,756}I missed that one! {Fade}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:37.90,0:14:38.48,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's pretty!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wanna do one too!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.81,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.90,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder if it'll go well...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone, over here! {Summer rains, you can never predict them}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.04,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's raining at a time like this...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:35.46,0:15:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It isn't stopping...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why did it have to rain...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:38.50,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's just an evening shower...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It'll stop soon.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:41.46,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I hope so...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways... isn't this great?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You have all these friends now.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:47.45,0:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's all thanks to you and Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You know... back when my CD came out...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Something like that happened as well...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And then...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When Meroko turned into me...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and started selling CDs...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I was wondering what would happen.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She had us in a bind there.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:10.41,0:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... it was for the best.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:12.70,0:16:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:14.08,0:16:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:14.78,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After hearing that...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Aren't you going to tell Meroko?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You found out?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.21,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The first friends I've ever made...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...were you and Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.24,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you two are very precious friends.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:35.85,0:16:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want you two to make up.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:49.49,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The rain stopped!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's keep going!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.81,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hazuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.78,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay. Let's launch the skyrockets!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do it! Do it!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:37.58,0:17:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.52,0:17:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Now, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\pos(320,15)}Go!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,465)}Go!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's so cute!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's a bunny and a cat!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-What's that?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I only made a bunny...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:02.81,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That girl...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto... I...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You... won't forgive me... will you?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.62,0:18:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Bye!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hold on!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't just assume what someone else is feeling.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... you'll forgive me?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's do that... you know?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:34.93,0:18:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's absurd to hide our name \Nwhen our cover is blown...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We... who will even lie to crying children...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:39.89,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The Shinigami Duo!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(70,450)}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.23,0:18:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(560,50)}Meroko!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(410,50)}With out powers combined... we are...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(230,450)}With out powers combined... we are...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:44.98,0:18:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an3}Spring Onion Ramen!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:44.98,0:18:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an1}Spring Onion Ramen!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:53.28,0:18:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:54.83,0:18:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is it, Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm glad that...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:57.82,0:19:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...that there were spring onion ramen fireworks... something like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.67,0:19:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you saying... silly Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What am I saying...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.35,0:19:15.44,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,450}Good night!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.84,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(212.571,450)}Good night!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(356.571,450)}Good night! {Mitsuki}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Be careful on the way home!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:19.35,0:19:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:22.35,0:19:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did everyone go home after having a good time?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.77,0:19:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:25.79,0:19:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's good.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, Mitsuki-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:29.17,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You are still recovering from your illness.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.00,0:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Dress warmly and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:34.56,0:19:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That is all.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Grandma.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks for always worrying about me!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,435}Takuto! Meroko!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,435}It looks like Grandma and me...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,435}...are going to get along just fine!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:55.59,0:19:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,435}Is that so?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,435}Sure is.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:35.64,0:21:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez! She's so {\i1}irritating{\i0} !
Dialogue: 2,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That Wakamatsu Madoka is back again!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.48,0:21:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.98,0:21:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why are you going so far as to call that Madoka an enemy?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:43.45,0:21:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She might be a surprisingly good person. {that's much later}
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's no way!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:46.45,0:21:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The one who tore apart her costume...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.41,0:21:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It was definitely that Madoka's doing!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:50.41,0:21:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This isn't the time to be saying that!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:53.58,0:21:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She goes back to work today!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:55.21,0:21:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We have to be there for her!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Next time on Full Moon wo Sagashite:
Dialogue: 2,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}New Feelings
Dialogue: 2,0:22:01.13,0:22:02.21,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look forward to it!
