Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:50.33,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,100)}Why... just why have I fallen in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:56.80,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\be3\fad(200,200)}Yet, still... I can't stop my tears from falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:27.95,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(166,100)}I lost way too much back then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:32.21,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I couldn't sing at all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:36.71,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,100)}That place you had to leave for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:44.30,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}It happened to be the place where I was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:50.68,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,100)}On that day I could see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:55.52,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}The desolation lying in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:01.11,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I wonder if it's the same for both of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:08.45,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,40)}If you would just notice, I'm always by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:14.46,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:20.46,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}Your voice is calling out with such sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:26.55,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,00)}I never knew what was supporting me, back then, and even now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:32.47,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,840)}Until we became so far apart...
